What's this

861
00:42:01,880 --> 00:42:04,600
This is a toy from the Western Regions that I brought from my house

862
00:42:04,600 --> 00:42:06,040
Made by divine craftsmen

863
00:42:06,040 --> 00:42:06,840
Look

864
00:42:07,640 --> 00:42:09,280
Just ring a bell

865
00:42:09,280 --> 00:42:11,000
Another bell will also vibrate.

866
00:42:12,560 --> 00:42:13,400
real

867
00:42:15,320 --> 00:42:17,480
Are you dealing with Zheng Jin this time?

868
00:42:17,480 --> 00:42:18,840
Be careful

869
00:42:18,840 --> 00:42:20,240
If any danger occurs

870
00:42:20,240 --> 00:42:21,400
Just ring the bell

871
00:42:21,760 --> 00:42:23,040
I will come to you immediately

872
00:42:23,640 --> 00:42:24,160
Remember?

873
00:42:25,440 --> 00:42:25,920
Remembered

874
00:42:30,280 --> 00:42:31,320
Eat quickly

875
00:42:40,080 --> 00:42:41,920
That’s almost the end of the show

876
00:42:41,920 --> 00:42:43,200
Don't push yourself too far

877
00:42:43,200 --> 00:42:45,080
Forgot your true identity

878
00:42:56,200 --> 00:42:57,600
It turned out to be him

879
00:42:58,600 --> 00:42:59,560
Fan Chengshou

880
00:42:59,560 --> 00:43:00,760
The eldest son is already waiting for you

881
00:43:01,320 --> 00:43:01,920
please

882
00:43:31,360 --> 00:43:33,160
Miss is saying

883
00:43:33,160 --> 00:43:34,320
Just there

884
00:43:34,320 --> 00:43:36,600
Someone passed by with a hiss.

885
00:43:37,960 --> 00:43:38,840
But

886
00:43:38,840 --> 00:43:40,520
I didn't see anyone

887
00:43:40,520 --> 00:43:43,120
I didn't hear a sound either.

888
00:43:44,080 --> 00:43:44,960
Go down

889
00:44:37,800 --> 00:44:38,760
private salt

890
00:44:43,440 --> 00:44:46,040
It's not a special smuggled item.

